## Helper commands

Import existing resources:

terragrunt import "github_repository.this[\"terraform-aws-sns\"]" terraform-aws-sns

# Optional imports (may not exist):
terragrunt import "github_branch_protection.this[\"terraform-aws-sns/master\"]" "terraform-aws-sns:master"
